{"tid":404671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青：搞獨立足以致命　慘烈戰爭都與統獨有關","createTime":"2017-09-18T09:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T10:55:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0030ec3b58293ffabdf372ca9694ae55bca0ce2","tid":404671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170918/s00001/c7f7a5fdb238dba0a4e921190e753eca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2Fc7f7a5fdb238dba0a4e921190e753eca.jpg&h=5475ee70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多間大專校園都出現「港獨」標語，中原集團創辦人施永青指出，「搞獨立是足以致命的」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青於《am730》專欄撰寫＜掛標語屬鼓吹　已超越言論自由＞文章，指掛標語與學術無關，而言論自由不是絕對，亦「不是完全無條件的」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青引用電影橋段作例，「常看到這樣的場景，母親用手捂住孩子的嘴巴，不讓孩子發聲，因為附近有掠食動物，或正式在搜捕他們的壞人。在這種情況下，不要說發言，連發聲也不可以」。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，為了避免危險而不應發言的情況是大量存在，「若果一個人的發言只會帶來他個人的危險，他還可以自行選擇；但若果他的言行還可以帶來其他人的禍害，其他人就可以制止他」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青又稱，人類歷史上很多慘烈戰爭，都與統一、獨立問題有關，如造成近百萬人傷亡的美國南北戰爭，表面上是為了解放黑奴，實際上是為了阻止南方獨立。他另舉例，有生活在英國的庫爾德族人，因為在土耳其與同學講了庫爾德族應有權獨立說話，差點被其他同學打死，惟學校不但沒有處罰打他的同學，反而把他開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n施永青指出，一旦涉及統獨問題，人類就會不理性，不惜以性命為代價，直言「搞獨立是足以致命的」，「香港的年輕人沒有這方面的經驗，又缺乏歷史知識，誤以為有言論自由就說什麼都可以&hellip;&hellip;他們不應該率性而為，也應該尊重其他人的意願，以及考慮到社會整體要付出的代價」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505717670862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505717670862&d=Y8qSumg6seHukszPxWBdZXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2482447a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505717670862&h=216d97ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505717670862</a>"},{"pid":"0786b145fadf9cd55bd22e23a5a615f917574d8c","tid":404671,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"c7c3cb5c4c53b4a971f8e1c65ec41da2fe163979","tid":404671,"uid":5616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"即係支共係壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bb7482df326786104cb67023cc9b10efcdb713","tid":404671,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"統獨，是咪統治獨裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94caabd489feecbf325a31bded079b7c4e7baf2","tid":404671,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"唔夠人講就屈人唔理性、唔識歷史，仲有無第二招？"},{"pid":"95ef1babe65a279467a862edf5efd6c75291d079","tid":404671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c88802631598cc61f6e0823dbad6a76e9c250e7","tid":404671,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係支共係壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係人都知 但邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a601093a6eee4a75ab317b6695d6541772ace9f1","tid":404671,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"寄張聖誕卡俾佢最和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89248dcb4c8562582dcd3902d347e2e716e2c661","tid":404671,"uid":76609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"佢冇講錯喎，佢冇話港獨唔岩，<br />\n只係你要講港獨，就隨時會俾人砌，<br />\n以前攪獨立係搵命搏，<br />\n而家班人講獨立當唱歌，<br />\n完全冇諗過後果"},{"pid":"d0fd9a3eef983cd5b76b08ef1632bf9e7267d944","tid":404671,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"施永青引用電影橋段作例，「常看到這樣的場景，母親用手捂住孩子的嘴巴，不讓孩子發聲，因為附近有掠食動物，或正式在搜捕他們的壞人。在這種情況下，不要說發言，連發聲也不可以」。<br />\n<br />\n除左最後果段例行踩鳩年輕人<br />\n屍生今次算係直線wor<br />\n<br />\n佢警告緊班後生仔要睇清楚共狗有幾恐怖<br />\n先去好夠膽搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9e7e45440e5b62a3ae37928b9d52a622a3cb7e","tid":404671,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"屌，老共都係打扙起家；不過，咁佢係咪直線話老共獨裁，現在蘇獨、愛獨、加獨同'灰'獨都公投喎"},{"pid":"ecf78bcb5c3f6df60eea900ee3a60ea080384e3c","tid":404671,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施永青引用電影橋段作例，「常看到這樣的場景，母親用手捂住孩子的嘴巴，不讓孩子發聲，因為附近有掠食動物，或正式在搜捕他們的壞人。在這種情況下，不要說發言，連發聲也不可以」。<br />\n<br />\n除左最後果段例行踩鳩年輕人<br />\n屍生今次算係直線wor<br />\n<br />\n佢警告緊班後生仔要睇清楚共狗有幾恐怖<br />\n先去好夠膽搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早就預計到啦<br />\n施生呢番說話 係14年既旺角已經有人講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271c3d3aa902f1c3f86a5cfe5c2eecc12b4f19f9","tid":404671,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"反証97回歸中國係錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3ee7938230fa18e71c00806ecd932cfcdcc056","tid":404671,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a92732eb49eed2ce88bf31c4cb31bc78dc8393e","tid":404671,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"好耐無見佢鳩噏"},{"pid":"d65f9818d9a73bc3207114ba38b4a314408d80e0","tid":404671,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"無產階級不要妄圖翻身做主，破壞香港社會繁榮穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecdbb41ded4c1c6fad4ff4396e8d122612d80dc","tid":404671,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017